posts.post_title: FS: Graded T Cards (T-200, T-206 & T-207)
posts.post_content:

T-200 Philadelphia NL (SGC 10) - $90
T-206 Duffy (GAI 2.5, American Beauty 460 Back) - SOLD
T-206 Elberfeld (PSA 1, Portrait Washington) - SOLD
T-206 Tannehill (PSA 1, Chicago Tannehill, Red Hindu Back) - SOLD
T-207 Ainsmith (PSA 4) - $70

Prices quoted include postage and handling.  EMAILS ONLY to [url]METaylor2001@hotmail.com[/url] -first email to say "I'll take it!" gets the card.  Scans included bellow.
